title constellation z
author stephen lavelle
homepage www.increpare.com

(a port of the first few levels of my game, the full version of which is 
http://ded.increpare.com/~locus/constellationz/
)

========
OBJECTS
========

Background
Black

BorderTile 
Red

Teleport 
white

target
blue
