.....

AltPlayer
Black

CanNotWin C
red

CanWin
red

=======
LEGEND
=======

# = BorderTile
. = Background
P = Player
O = Teleport
t = target


=========
SOUNDS
=========
sfx1 44641500 (teleport)
startgame 26858107
startlevel 34443107
endlevel 34292905

================
COLLISIONLAYERS
================

Background
CannotWin, CanWin
Teleport,BorderTile, target
Player, AltPlayer

======
RULES     
======     

late [ player Teleport ] -> [ altplayer Teleport ] sfx1

late [ altplayer Teleport ] [ Teleport no altplayer ] -> [altplayer teleport] [Teleport player ]
late [altplayer ] -> []

late [ player bordertile ] -> cancel

(the win condition for this game is:
all players have to be on all exit points

right now this can't be stated as a win condition, which is dumb, so here's my hacky workaround)

late [player] [cannotwin] -> [player] [canwin]
late [canwin] [ player no target]-> [cannotwin] [ player no target]
late [canwin] [ target no player] ->[cannotwin] [target no player]
late [canwin] -> win

==============
WINCONDITION
==============

